title: Complete the Square
text: Group $$x$$ and $$y$$ terms and complete the square: $$4\left(x^2-2x\right)+9\left(y^2-8y\right)=-112$$.

title: Convert to Standard Form
text: After completing the square: $$\frac{\left(x-1\right)^2}{9}$$ + $$\frac{\left(y-4\right)^2}{16}$$ $$=$$ $$1$$, then use $$a^2$$ $$=$$ $$16$$, $$b^2$$ $$=$$ $$9$$ to identify features.
